{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"This is a picture of a sunset on Mars"},{"time":3600,"text":"taken by NASA's Curiosity rover in 2013."},{"time":7960,"text":"Mars is a very cold planet,"},{"time":9840,"text":"flooded with high levels of UV radiation"},{"time":12120,"text":"and extremely dry."},{"time":14040,"text":"In fact, Mars is considered\nto be too dry for life as we know it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18960,"text":"I'm an astrobiologist."},{"time":20200,"text":"I try to understand\nthe origin of life on Earth"},{"time":23120,"text":"and the possibilities of finding life"},{"time":25360,"text":"elsewhere in the universe."},{"time":27400,"text":"People sometimes ask me,"},{"time":28680,"text":"how can you be an astrobiologist"},{"time":30880,"text":"if you don't have your own spaceship?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":33640,"text":"Well, what I do is that I study life"},{"time":35880,"text":"in those environments on Earth"},{"time":37880,"text":"that most closely resemble\nother interesting places in the universe."},{"time":42120,"text":"All life on Earth requires water,"},{"time":44600,"text":"so in my case I focus\non the intimate relationship"},{"time":47160,"text":"between water and life"},{"time":48680,"text":"in order to understand"},{"time":50280,"text":"if we could find life\nin a planet as dry as Mars."},{"time":54440,"text":"But since I do not have\nthe 2.5 billion dollars"},{"time":58000,"text":"to send my own robot to Mars,"},{"time":60240,"text":"I study the most Martian place on Earth,"},{"time":63200,"text":"the Atacama Desert."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64760,"text":"Located in northern Chile,"},{"time":66440,"text":"it is the oldest\nand driest desert on Earth."},{"time":70080,"text":"To give you an idea of how dry it is,"},{"time":72080,"text":"consider here in Vancouver it rains\nover 1,000 millimeters of rain every year."},{"time":77880,"text":"In the Atacama, there are places\nwith no reported rains"},{"time":81520,"text":"in the last 400 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84880,"text":"How do I know this?"},{"time":86600,"text":"Well, because I was born\nand raised in the Atacama --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":90120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91760,"text":"So I had a unique advantage"},{"time":93800,"text":"when I started studying this desert."},{"time":96880,"text":"So let me tell you guys\na few fantastic examples"},{"time":100440,"text":"he has found"},{"time":102120,"text":"on how life has adapted\nto live with almost no water at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106640,"text":"One of my first findings\nwas in the entrance of a cave"},{"time":109240,"text":"facing the Pacific Ocean."},{"time":111000,"text":"In this place, we reported\na new type of microalgae"},{"time":114720,"text":"that grew only on top of the spiderwebs\nthat covered the cave entrance."},{"time":119240,"text":"Have you ever seen a spiderweb\nearly in the morning?"},{"time":123200,"text":"It's covered with dew,"},{"time":124800,"text":"so this microalgae learned\nthat in order to carry photosynthesis"},{"time":128080,"text":"in the coast of the driest\ndesert on Earth,"},{"time":131120,"text":"they could use the spiderwebs."},{"time":132640,"text":"So here they may access\nthe water from the fogs"},{"time":135080,"text":"that regularly cover\nthese areas in the morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138640,"text":"In another cave, we found\na different type of microalgae."},{"time":142120,"text":"This one is able to use ocean mist\nas a source of water,"},{"time":146360,"text":"and strikingly lives\nin the very bottom of a cave,"},{"time":149520,"text":"so it has adapted to live\nwith less than 0.1 percent"},{"time":152760,"text":"of the amount of light\nthat regular plants need."},{"time":157000,"text":"These type of findings\nsuggest to me that on Mars,"},{"time":160040,"text":"we may find even\nphotosynthetic life inside caves."},{"time":162920,"text":"And by the way, that's me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":167160,"text":"Now, for almost 15 years\nthis region of Yungay, discovered by NASA,"},{"time":172920,"text":"was thought to be\nthe driest place of this desert,"},{"time":175960,"text":"but I knew that it was not."},{"time":177720,"text":"How? You already know the answer."},{"time":180120,"text":"Because I was born\nand raised in this desert."},{"time":182360,"text":"So I remembered that I\nusually see fogs in Yungay,"},{"time":187040,"text":"so after setting sensors\nin a number of places,"},{"time":189280,"text":"where I remember\nnever seeing fogs or clouds,"},{"time":192360,"text":"I reported four other sites\nmuch drier than Yungay,"},{"time":196400,"text":"with this one, Mar√≠a Elena South,"},{"time":199040,"text":"being the truly driest place on Earth,"},{"time":202520,"text":"as dry as Mars,"},{"time":204520,"text":"and amazingly, just a 15-minute ride"},{"time":206880,"text":"from the small mining town\nwhere I was born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"Now, in this search, we were trying\nto actually find the dry limit"},{"time":213440,"text":"for life on Earth,"},{"time":214680,"text":"a place so dry that nothing\nwas able to survive in it."},{"time":218560,"text":"But even here, well hidden underground,"},{"time":221160,"text":"we found a number\nof different microorganisms,"},{"time":223600,"text":"which suggested to me\nthat similarly dry places, like Mars,"},{"time":227080,"text":"may be inhabited."},{"time":229360,"text":"We even have some preliminary evidences"},{"time":231680,"text":"that these microorganisms\nmay still be active"},{"time":234240,"text":"in the desiccated state,"},{"time":236200,"text":"like walking mummies all around us,"},{"time":240040,"text":"and that they may be using\nUV radiation as a source of energy."},{"time":244880,"text":"If confirmed, this would have\na huge impact on our definition of life,"},{"time":249480,"text":"on how we look for life\nelsewhere in the universe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252760,"text":"Due to its clear skies, by 2020,"},{"time":255800,"text":"60 percent of the biggest\ntelescopes on Earth"},{"time":258480,"text":"will be located in the Atacama,"},{"time":260720,"text":"and while everyone else\nwill be looking among the stars"},{"time":263640,"text":"to answer the question, \"Are we alone?\""},{"time":266800,"text":"I will be looking down to the ground"},{"time":268720,"text":"searching for this same answer"},{"time":271320,"text":"in my own backyard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272960,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}